description:
It's time for the third of our Manchester Jazz Festival // NQ Jazz podcasts, featuring saxophonist extraordinaire Iain Ballamy!

Head over to ballamy.com to check out all of Iain's projects & recordings, and head over to patreon.com/nqjazz to check out our full digital programme!

A huge thanks to our Patreon patrons and Arts Council England for helping make our programme possible!
